## 懒羊羊的数学题
今天村长给小羊们留了一些列竖式加法数学题，懒羊羊根本没看题就去睡觉了，等到转天上课前十分钟他才开始看题，然而那些题目的数字极大，位数极多，让懒羊羊感到头晕目眩，你能帮助他在上课前完成作业题吗(所有样例的正负号都相同，但是会有负号）
- 输入两个字符串代表两个数字，完成两个大数的加法
- 输出大数加的结果
- 完成参考代码中的重载加法运算符即可
- 参考代码
```
#include<iostream>
#include<cmath>
#include<string>
using namespace std;
class INT
{
public:
	int* data;//存放每一位的数字的int数组，第0位存放个位，第1位存放十位，以此类推
	int size;//数字有多少位
	int fuhao;//正负号
	INT(int x)
	{
		data = new int[4000];
		for (int i = 0; i < 4000; i++)
			data[i] = 0;
		if (x == 0) {
			size = 1; fuhao = 1; return;
		}
		fuhao = x / fabs(x);
		x = fabs(x);
		size = 0;
		while (x != 0)
		{
			data[size++] = x % 10;
			x /= 10;
		}
	}
	INT()
	{
		data = new int[4000] ;
		for (int i = 0; i < 4000; i++)
			data[i] = 0;
		size = 1;
		fuhao = 1;
	}
	~INT()
	{
		delete[]data;
	}
	INT(const INT& in)
	{
		data = new int[4000];
		for (int i = 0; i < 4000; i++)
			data[i] = 0;
		size = in.size;
		for (int i = 0; i < size; i++)
			data[i] = in.data[i];
		fuhao = in.fuhao;
	}
	INT(string str)
	{
		data = new int[4000] ;
		for (int i = 0; i < 4000; i++)
			data[i] = 0;
		size = str.size();
		fuhao = 1;
		int i = 0;
		for (int j = size - 1; j >= 0; j--)
		{
			if (str[j] != '-')
			{
				data[i++] = str[j] - '0';
			}
		}
		if (str[0] == '-') { fuhao = -1; size--; }
	}
	void operator=(const INT& in)
	{
		delete data;
		data = new int[4000] ;
		for (int i = 0; i < 4000; i++)
			data[i] = 0;
		size = in.size;
		for (int i = 0; i < size; i++)
		{
			data[i] = in.data[i];
		}
		fuhao = in.fuhao;
	}
	void clear()
	{
		delete data;
		size = 0;
		fuhao = 1;
		data = new int[4000] ;
		for (int i = 0; i < 4000; i++)
			data[i] = 0;
	}
};
ostream& operator<<(ostream& os,INT& in)
{
	if (in.fuhao < 0) cout << "-";
	for (int i = in.size - 1; i >= 0; i--)
	{
		os << in.data[i];
	}
	return os;
}
INT operator+(INT in1,INT in2) 
{
	
}
int main()
{
	string str;
	cin >> str;
	INT i1(str);
	str.clear();
	cin >> str;
	INT i2(str);
	INT i3;
	i3 = i1 + i2;
	cout << i3;
	return 0;
}
```
